STARTING THE MULTI-PLAYER GAME
----------------------

UI to play as Player 0:
cargo run -- -p galaxy --state
1101100101111101100011110101100110011001100111101110001001000101101111101011101111000001001101101001110000
--steps '(45,0) (45,19)'

UI to play as Player 1:
cargo run -- -p galaxy --state 1101100101111101100011110101100110011001100111101110001001000101101111101011101111000001001101101001110000 --steps '(45,0) (45,-19)'


Look for the following debug output :
    Received POST response:
    [1, [[0, <bignumber>], [1, <bignumber>]]]

Copy the number for the non-UI player as <player_key> into either of the following AI command lines:

    AI with proxy:
    cargo run -- --proxy https://icfpc2020-api.testkontur.ru <player_key>

    AI interactively with proxy:
    cargo run -- --interactive --proxy https://icfpc2020-api.testkontur.ru <player_key>

Then type the following into the UI to start the game:

UI is Player 0:
    205 40

UI is Player 1:
    205 3
